title: Our Commander[ette?] in Chief
body: I'm probably going to disappear for <a href="http://travis.servebeer.com/blog.net/archive/2004/06/02/the_most_powerful_man_in_the_world_almost_choked_to_death_on_a_pretzel.aspx">making fun of Bush twice in a row</a>, but oh well:<br/>"I want to thank my friend, Sen. Bill Frist, for joining us today. … He married a Texas girl, I want you to know. (Laughter.) Karyn is with us. A West Texas girl, just like me."—Nashville, Tenn., May 27, 2004
bodyArticleHtml:
2004-06-02

Our Commander[ette?] in Chief

I want to thank my friend, Sen. Bill Frist, for joining us today. … He married a Texas girl, I want you to know. (Laughter.) Karyn is with us. A West Texas girl, just like me.
